title: BiPro USA to participate in FNCE® 2015
text:
Information contained on this page is provided by an independent third-party content provider. WorldNow and this Station make no warranties or representations in connection therewith. If you have any questions or comments about this page please contact pressreleases@worldnow.com .
SOURCE BiPro USA
EDEN PRAIRIE, Minn. , Oct. 2, 2015 /PRNewswire/ -- BiPro USA will exhibit its BiPro ® whey protein isolate at the Food & Nutrition Conference & Expo (FNCE) from October 4-6 . The event, featuring many of the world's leading food and nutrition companies, will take place at the Nashville, Tennessee , Music City Center.
Unflavored BiPro contains zero fats, carbohydrates or sugars and is comprised of just two ingredients : whey protein isolate and sunflower lecithin. BiPro's purity makes it an ideal supplement to mix with food . Chocolate chip cookies made with whey protein isolate will be at BiPro USA's booth (No. 607) for guests to sample. Jenna Stangland , MS, RD, LDN, will also be at the booth to answer any nutrition-related questions pertaining to BiPro.
A floor plan of the conference is available at the FNCE 2015 website .
BiPro USA is the consumer division of Davisco, business unit of Agropur inc. To learn more about the importance of lean, clean protein visit our FAQ page.
